Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不被他的精神控制影响  将小屋变为比尔的禁区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}from his mental tricks. A way to Bill-proof the shack.
