Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.81,0:03:37.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,洒点水银  我再想想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}sprinkle some mercury, and let's see,
