Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,独角兽鬃毛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Unicorn hair.
