Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没希望了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's hopeless.
