Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:52.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身负魔法重任前往的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}by a pure, good-hearted person who goes on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能获取它的鬃毛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}a magical quest to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿福叔公  求求你让我去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Grunkle Ford, can I please go on this quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对独角兽可是超级超级痴迷啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I am literally obsessed with unicorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:02.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我生下来会说的第一个词就是独角兽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My first word was unicorn,
