Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创造了自己的独角兽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to a horse's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你再看看我现在穿的是什么毛衣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Are you even looking at the sweater I'm wearing right now?
