Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她说得好有道理  -我竟无法反驳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- That's true. She has a point. - Can't argue there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那总能让我去找独角兽鬃毛了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So can I go on a mission to get that hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求您了  求您了  让我洒热血都行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Please, please, please. I'll give you my blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.09,0:04:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  取毛路布满了艰难险阻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Very well, but it won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-带上这个  和这个  -哇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Take this, and this. - Ooh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:29.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太长时间没在这个时空待过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I haven't been in this dimension for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.87,0:04:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给小孩子武器不会有什么事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's okay to give children weapons, right?
