Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:37.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑  是条子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's the cops. Gun it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糖糖  格兰达  温蒂  把下午的时间腾出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Candy, Grenda, Wendy, clear the afternoon.
