Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎不可能  我跟独角兽打过交道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Unlikely. I've dealt with unicorns before,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果让我用一个字描述他们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and if I had to describe them in one word,
