Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.79,0:04:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那我们该怎么防范比尔呢  -跟我来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- So what are we gonna do about Bill? - Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到我的私人研究室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Welcome to my private study.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.14,0:05:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个地方藏有我最古老和最隐秘的知识\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The place where I keep my most ancient and secret knowledge.
