Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪普  快跟上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Dipper, come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果小屋没法成为比尔的禁区\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If we can't Bill-proof the shack,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.28,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就只能退求其次了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}we're gonna have to do the next best thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们的思维无法被比尔读取\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're gonna have to Bill-proof our minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算能出任务真是高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's nice to finally be out on a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有我们这些姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Just us gals.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不是来和闺蜜聊天的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Forget the gal talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来这儿是看  摸  甚至变成一只独角兽的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm here to meet, touch, and/or become a unicorn.
