Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.88,0:05:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我关心我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}because I care about my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.28,0:05:51.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  我大概五岁的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Honestly, I stopped believing in unicorns
