Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.29,0:06:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙女美甲店在那边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The fairy nail salon is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里说如果要召唤独角兽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It says to summon the unicorn,
