Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:13.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吟唱古老的韵字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}droned only by the deepest-voiced druids of old.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}On it.
