Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受挑战\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll take that bet.
