Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:07:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临我这迷人的房间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hark. Visitors to my room of enchantment.
