Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  梅宝  你是坏人并不是我的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm sorry, Mabel. It's not my fault you're a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.45,0:11:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅宝  等等  快回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mabel, wait. Come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.92,0:11:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话我先失陪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now if you'll excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.36,0:11:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三点钟的时候我要在彩虹前摆造型\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I have a 3:00 posing in front of a rainbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  梅宝  别被这种事打击到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Come on, Mabel. Don't beat yourself up over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还是忘记那可笑的独角兽鬃毛吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's forget about getting that dumb unicorn hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐妹们  这已经不再是鬃毛的问题了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's not about the hair anymore, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是我这个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.64,0:11:21.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲切和善良才是我存在的意义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Being kind and sweet is what makes me who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不再是好人  那我是谁呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If I'm not a good person, who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要想出一件好事  能让我变得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm not leaving this spot until I think of a deed
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.95,0:11:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像瑟拉斯贝拉贝莎贝一样好  否则绝不离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}that makes me as good as Celestabellabethabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.45,0:11:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是梅宝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But Mabel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:31.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我一个人静静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Just leave me be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.72,0:11:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹们  要我说  这件事对她来说是个沉重的负担\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Guys, if you ask me, this whole thing is a serious load.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅宝算是我见过最好的人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mabel's, like, the best person I've ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经尝试过以善意的方式去取得毛发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We tried getting that hair the good way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.60,0:11:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在该采用温蒂的方式了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now it's time we try the Wendy way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在建议我们使用暴力  搞破坏吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Are you suggesting violence? Sabotage?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.00,0:11:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做梅宝不会喜欢的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mabel's not going to like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅宝根本不需要知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mabel doesn't need to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.24,0:11:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  是时候该摒弃完美主义的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Look, it's time we stopped trying to be so "Perfect,"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做回我们自己了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and be who we really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是狂野  愤怒  凶猛的动物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're crazed, angry, sweaty animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是独角兽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're not unicorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.95,0:12:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're women!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想要什么就必须搞到手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And we take what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-说得好  -没错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Yeah! - Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.39,0:12:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是太过了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会儿我们这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Here's what we're gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我来一大壶最香甜的金银花酒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get me a flagon of your daintiest honeysuckle, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要检查一下你的身份证件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm gonna need to see some I.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是条子  快卧倒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The cops. Hit the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在找一个知道怎么撂倒独角兽的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm lookin' for someone who knows how to take down a unicorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.31,0:12:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别想耍花招\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No tricks or games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是人类   我们要什么就必须搞到手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We are human. We take what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙尘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Fairy dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一整袋仙尘足够让一只独角兽睡得死死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A whole magic bag's enough to put a unicorn out cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要我帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but if I do you a favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.43,0:12:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们得为我做点事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}you gotta do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说吧  矮子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Just spill it, half-pint.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:50.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在森林本区  蝴蝶交易是非法的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Butterfly trafficking is illegal in this part of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我很喜欢蝴蝶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I like butterflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在我脸上挠痒痒  弄得我大笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They tickle my face and make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我一袋蝴蝶  我们就做交易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Bring me a bag of butterflies, and we got a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两袋仙尘  我们说好了的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Two bags of fairy dust, just like we agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你从哪里搞来的这玩意儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Where do you get this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.29,0:13:16.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人人爱吃香肠  却没人关心香肠的做法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Everyone likes sausage, but no one likes to know how it's made.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:17.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真恶心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You disgust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:19.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们拿魔药  我拿蝴蝶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You've got your poison, I've got mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们公平交易\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We made a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  交易结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yeah, well, the deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准动  你被捕了  趴下  趴下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Freeze. You're under arrest. Get down, get down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些蝴蝶不是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}These butterflies aren't mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.30,0:13:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓  我是被陷害的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I swear. I've been framed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟被我们打扮成法官的可爱猫头鹰说去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Tell it to the adorable owl we've dressed as a judge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.34,0:13:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的那份呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs21}帮斯坦削铅笔  灌满蜂蜜罐  给苏斯织围巾  给猫刷毛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:36.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好事  好事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Good deeds, good deeds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不够好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh, that's not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  梅宝  你可以做得更好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Come on, Mabel, you can do better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\a6\fs21}嘶叫，祈祷，小跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我当然也想去旅游\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh, sure, sure. I wish I could travel,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是当前的经济状况又不允许\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but it's just not feasible in this economy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞啥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What the hay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡觉吧  快睡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sleep now. Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  等等  停下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梅宝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Mabel, sh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会吵醒她的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You'll wake her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但姐妹们  这是在做坏事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But this is wrong, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.38,0:14:12.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可保护神秘小屋是件好事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But protecting the shack is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的眼睛看错了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Doth my eyes deceive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永远也也得不到纯洁之心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You shall never be pure of heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  你不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, you don't understand.
