Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我年轻的时候  也应该多像你这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I should've been more like you when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.74,0:17:56.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迪普  我真是傻  还准备遮掩这些事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Dipper, I was a fool to try to hide all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我急着让你做好准备对付比尔的诡计\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The reason I've been trying to prepare you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.87,0:18:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我曾经上过比尔的当\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}for Bill's tricks is because Bill tricked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.27,0:18:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我人生中最愧疚的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's the biggest regret of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.57,0:18:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比尔一开始并不是我的敌人  迪普\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Bill wasn't always my enemy, Dipper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.25,0:18:07.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经以为他是我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I used to think he was my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:09.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久很久以前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}long, long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对重力泉的研究遇到了瓶颈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I had hit a roadblock in my investigation of Gravity Falls,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.02,0:18:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我在一个洞穴里找到了一些神秘的文字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}until I found some mysterious writing in a cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是关于一个无所不知的生物的古老咒语\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ancient incantations about a being with answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它警告我不要读那些文字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It warned me not to read them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我当时已经孤注一掷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but I was desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.60,0:18:26.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大声读出了那些铭文  不过什么也没有发生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I read the inscription aloud, but nothing happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.30,0:18:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到那天午后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}until later that afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.24,0:18:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了一个古怪至极的梦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}when I had the most peculiar dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好呀  聪明的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hiya, smart guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别被我吓得心脏病发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Whoa, don't have a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没到九十二岁呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're not 92 yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.30,0:18:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫比尔  你叫斯坦福・派恩斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Name's Bill, and your name's Stanford Pines,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.16,0:18:51.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个改变了世界的男人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the man who changed the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我言之过早了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I'm getting ahead of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松  想不想下一轮跨次元象棋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's relax. Care for a game of interdimensional chess?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者喝杯茶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Have a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:01.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他告诉我他是个灵感之神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He told me he was a muse,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他每个世纪都会选择一个才华横溢的人触发灵感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}that he chose one brilliant mind a century to inspire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是个傻瓜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What a fool I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被他的花言巧语和诡计蒙蔽了双眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Blinded by his flattery and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他成为了我的研究助手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He became my research assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.98,0:19:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可以随他所愿  自由地进出我的脑海\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He was free to move in and out of my mind as he pleased;
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是伙伴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}we were partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当他告诉我  我可以建一个通向其他世界的门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When he told me that I could complete my research
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来完成我的研究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}by building a gateway to other worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.84,0:19:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信了他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I trusted him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.96,0:19:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说这就是造就天才的方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He said this was the way genius happened--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.83,0:19:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上朋友的一点儿小帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}with a little help from a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:32.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去我似乎离人生最大的成就\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It seemed that I was on the verge
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:34.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一步之遥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}of my greatest achievement.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我的研究伙伴瞥见了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Until my partner got a glimpse
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比尔真正的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}of Bill's true plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比尔  你骗了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Bill, you lied to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个传送门到底通向哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Where does that portal really lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来超级天才先生终于变得聪明了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Looks like Mr. Brainiac finally got smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说吧  当传送门完成充能的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's just say that when that portal finishes charging up,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的时空就知道什么叫热闹啦  对吗  伙计们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}your dimension is gonna learn how to party, right, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我会阻止你的  我会关上这扇门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No. I'll stop you. I'll shut it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:19:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵守约定吧  六指\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A deal's a deal, sixer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你无法阻止我们两个世界之间纽带的形成\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You can't stop the bridge between our world from coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是看着你努力尝试  很有趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But it would be fun to watch you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至是傻的可爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Cute even.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被背叛了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'd been betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:09.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我关掉了传送门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I shut the portal down,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切断了比尔的世界和我们世界之间的连接\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}severing the link between Bill's world and ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不得不把我的操作指南藏起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I had to hide my instructions
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.01,0:20:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就再也没有人能完成比尔的研究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}so no one could ever finish Bill's work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自那以后  比尔就在等待传送门重新开启\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Bill's been waiting for the gateway to reopen ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它要做的仅仅是触碰这个裂痕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All he needs to do is get his hands on this rift.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对比尔而言  这是一场游戏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}To Bill, it's just a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:27.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是对我们来说  可能意味着我们世界的毁灭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But to us, it would mean the end of our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是天大的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Oh, man" Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对之前的事感到很尴尬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm so embarrassed about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是个白痴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始  我们之间再也不会有秘密了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}From now on, no more secrets between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.14,0:20:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子  咱俩不是头两个被比尔耍的白痴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We're not the first two idiots to be tricked by Bill, boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:47.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果我们一同合作  我们会是最后的两个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but if we work together, we could be the last.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是比尔怎么办  我弄坏了那个机器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But what about Bill? I broke the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.05,0:20:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们没办法保护小屋了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now we have no way to protect the shack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:57.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才是有人说到独角兽鬃毛吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Did someone say unicorn hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.32,0:20:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上  没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Uh, no, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是说了就完美了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Oh. That would've been perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓  反正我们拿到独角兽的鬃毛啦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Either way, we got some unicorn hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:06.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有独角兽的眼泪  独角兽的睫毛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Also some unicorn tears, unicorn eyelashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.76,0:21:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后还给了我们这个珠宝箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They finally gave us this treasure chest
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请我们离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to get rid of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs17}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It can't be.
